          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activation counting of radiochemically",
                "separated fission products. A source of einsteinium",
                "containing masses 253, 254 and 255 was obtained from",
                "the Transuranium Element Production Program at Oak",
                "Ridge National Laboratory. 255Fm is in secular",
                "equilibrium with 255Es was separated from parent",
                "einsteinium isotope. After removal it was deposited",
                "on platinum disks for irradiations. The 252Cf sources",
                "were formed from the alpha-decay of 255Fm."
              ]
            }
          ],
